<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM 1.3.1">
<l>pattuṭai yaṭiyavark keḷiyavaṉ piṟarkaḷuk kariya</l>
<l>vittakaṉ malarmakaḷ virumpumnam marumpeṟa laṭikaṇ</l>
<l>mattuṟu kaṭaiveṇṇey kaḷaviṉi luraviṭai yāppuṇ</l>
<l>ṭettiṟa muraliṉō ṭiṇaintirun tēṅkiya veḷivē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who is easy [to reach] for [his] devout servants, is for others a difficult</l>
<l>mysterious person; the flower lady desires the feet difficult to reach for us –</l>
<l>oh the ease with which he sobbed, staying joined to the mortar – in which manner? –</l>
<l>after having been tied by [his] strong waist for the theft of butter which trickled when experiencing the churning rod.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
